---
// SDGs Contribution Section
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        SDGsへの貢献
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        環境とキャリアを両立
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- SDG 12: Responsible Consumption and Production -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">12</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">つくる責任 つかう責任</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">ペーパーレス化</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">年間300枚の紙削減</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">持続可能な消費</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- SDG 10: Reduced Inequalities -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">10</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">人や国の不平等をなくそう</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">4言語対応</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">国際案件での不平等解消</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">言語バリアの解消</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- SDG 17: Partnerships for the Goals -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">17</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">パートナーシップで目標を達成しよう</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">名刺交換を通じた共創</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">グローバルなつながり</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">技術革新の共有</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Environmental Impact Summary -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">環境への配慮</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">300枚</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">年間削減される紙の枚数</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">100%</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">ペーパーレス化の実現</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">∞</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">更新可能なデジタル名刺</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-6">
          持続可能なビジネス活動で、地球環境とビジネス成長を両立
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
